text:
1. Hold knitting needles
2. Cast on stitches
3. Insert right needle into first stitch
4. Wrap yarn around right needle
5. Pull right needle through stitch
6. Slip stitch off left needle
7. Repeat steps 3-6 for each stitch
8. Continue knitting rows
9. Change yarn color if desired
10. Bind off stitches
11. Cut yarn
12. Weave in loose ends
